    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "A really appealing, honest classic in good overall condition and a great choice for someone who wants something they can enjoy right away without taking on a project. It presents nicely, runs and drives well, and has the kind of solid, well-kept feel that makes it easy to be proud of and comfortable to use. Not a concours car, but a genuinely good example with plenty of charm and a lot to like.",
