    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. A practical choice for someone seeking an inexpensive car for daily errands, a backup vehicle, or a starter project. Straightforward, accessible, and easy on the wallet\u2014an excellent opportunity to get on the road without overspending.",
      "price": 4995.0,
