      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest, affordable motoring here\u2014this car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a lot of value for someone who needs a dependable budget ride, a handy spare, or a solid little project. A great chance to get behind the wheel without spending big money. Priced to sell and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver with solid bones and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls well, the transmission goes through the gears as it should, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it an ideal budget commuter, shop truck, or easy project. Shows its age cosmetically and will want some TLC, but it\u2019s complete, presentable, and offers a lot of value for someone who appreciates a dependable platform they can sort as they go. Priced to move and worth a look if you want affordable transportation with real potential.",
      "price": 5950.0,
